test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -1 == -41
 +  where -1 = <built-in function prod>([-1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (2 == 3)
 +  where 2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7c75dc8dea80>([-41])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7c75dc8dea80> = [[1], [1, -41], [-41, 1], [-41, 1, -41], [1], [1, -41], ...].count
